  "title": "Library Assistant - East Region (Tampines)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Contract Duration: </strong>Until 31 May 2026</p><p><strong>Work Location: </strong>Tampines Changkat CC</p><p><strong>Work Hours: </strong>8:00 AM – 11:00 AM, Mon–Sun, 2–5 days/week depending on roster and operational needs<br /></p><p><strong>Hourly Pay:  $14 per hour</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description: </strong></p><ul><li><p>Receive, check, and sign off on delivered items; report discrepancies when necessary</p></li><li><p>Scan, process, and reshelve returned books, ensuring shelves are neat and sufficiently stocked</p></li><li><p>Conduct stocktakes and consolidate books for rework or follow-up actions</p></li><li><p>Test library gantries and assist with basic maintenance when required</p></li><li><p>Liaise with internal stakeholders on waiver requests, claims, and disputes via relevant systems</p></li><li><p>Provide basic customer service and handle simple enquiries</p></li><li><p>Perform any other duties as assigned<br /><br /><br /><br />Interested candidates, kindly email your resume to: charmaine.kok@tg-hr.com</p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p></li></ul>",
